The paper deals with the problem of reducing communication overhead in distributed machine learning, which is a core problem in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also proposes a new algorithm for constructing coresets, which involves clustering and optimization, making it relevant to categories such as cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also deals with optimization problems, which is relevant to categories such as cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.IT (Information Theory).
